body:
I believe the below code should issue warning/error as the argument types don't match (Formal --. Actual). Icarus does not show any error (Other tool does). 

>> 
```verilog
`define UVM_REG_ADDR_W 32

package t_pkg;

  typedef bit unsigned [`UVM_REG_ADDR_W - 1 : 0] uvm_reg_addr_t;

  function void get_csr_addrs ( uvm_reg_addr_t csr_addr_q [$]);
  endfunction : get_csr_addrs 

endpackage : t_pkg

module m;

  import t_pkg::*;

  bit [3:0] addr_q [$];

  initial begin
    get_csr_addrs (addr_q);
  end
endmodule : m

```
Thanks
Srini

